{{Orphan|date=August 2016}}
'''Percolate''' is a clubbing brand based in [[London|London, England]]. Founded in 2012, it is best known for [[Electronic music|Electronic Music]] events, specifically [[House music|House]], [[Disco]] and [[Techno]].<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://guestlist.net/article/88309/percolate-is-ready-to-party|title=Percolate is ready to party|last=Haycock|first=Annalisa|date=2015-08-13|website=guestlist.net|access-date=2016-04-22}}</ref> Founded by Fred Letts and Ed Lo Bianco, and now run by Letts and Simon Denby, Percolate is famously nomadic, utilising different venues across the capital for each edition.<ref name=":0" /> Events began at the 250 capacity [[Brixton]] venue [https://www.residentadvisor.net/club.aspx?id=87844 AIRspace], and have since taken in many of London's premier [[underground music]] venues including [http://www.villageunderground.co.uk/ Village Underground], [http://www.shapeshackney.com/ Shapes], [http://www.ovalspace.co.uk/ Oval Space], [http://www.corsicastudios.com/ Corsica Studios] and the 3000 capacity [https://www.residentadvisor.net/club.aspx?id=74592 Studio 338.]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.residentadvisor.net/promoter.aspx?id=32077&show=events|title=RA: Percolate|website=Resident Advisor|access-date=2016-04-22}}</ref> [[File:Percolate Neon Sign.jpg|thumb|Photograph from an early event]] Notable festival appearances include Gottwood, Love International (formerly Garden Festival) & [[Lovebox Festival]]. Percolate's 2016 Spring Series also included events in [[Manchester]] & [[Amsterdam]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.residentadvisor.net/news.aspx?id=32585|title=Percolate outlines 2016 schedule with DJ Sprinkles, Gerd Janson|website=Resident Advisor|access-date=2016-04-22}}</ref> In addition, a collaboration with Ibiza's [http://thezooproject.com/ Zoo Project] will see shows in Barcelona during [https://sonar.es/en/2016/ Sonar] week and a September Ibiza date.
== Notable Past Acts == * Bicep * [[Bonobo (musician)|Bonobo]] * [[Floating Points]] * Gerd Janson * Jeremy Underground * [[Leon Vynehall]] * Midland * [[Mount Kimbie]] * [[Moodymann]]
